Description:
  This generator creates a skeleton structure for a Samson Plugin

Example:
  rails generate plugin Thing

  This will create:
    plugins/thing/app/assets/javascript/
    plugins/thing/app/assets/stylesheets/
    plugins/thing/app/models/
    plugins/thing/db/migrate
    plugins/thing/lib/samson_plugin.rb
    plugins/thing/test/test_helper.rb
    plugins/thing/samson_thing.gemspec

